  "notes": "Single-file local-state navigation between three polished pages; no external UI libraries or Tailwind. Layout includes responsive sidebar/topbar, hero, metric cards, and Thompson routing mock data with all required model names. Build should work with standard Vite React + TypeScript setup via npm install && npm run build."
}
